  {
    Package~ "#1"~ is~ too~ old. \\
    The~ fduthesis~ class~ only~ supports~ "#1"~ with~ a~ version \\
    higher~ than~ v#2. \\\\
    Please~ update~ an~ up-to-date~ version~ of~ it~ using~ your \\
    TeX~ package~ manager~ or~ from~ CTAN.
  }
